# Project Context: Property Management Web Application

## Project Overview
This is a Next.js 16 property management web application built with TypeScript, featuring authentication, routing middleware, role-based access control (RBAC), and a modern UI with Tailwind CSS. The application uses Supabase for authentication, database, and authorization services. Recently enhanced with unified company management, admin invitation system, and page transition animations.

## Technology Stack
- **Framework**: Next.js 16.1.6 (App Router)
- **Language**: TypeScript 5+ (Strict Mode Enabled)
- **Styling**: Tailwind CSS v4
- **Authentication**: Supabase SSR (@supabase/ssr)
- **UI Components**: Custom components with Lucide React icons
- **Fonts**: Geist Sans & Geist Mono (optimized via next/font)
- **Package Manager**: npm

