### Database Schema (Current)

**auth.users table** (Supabase Auth):
| Column | Type | Description |
|--------|------|-------------|
| id | UUID | Primary key, auto-generated |
| email | string | User's email address |
| phone | string | E.164 formatted phone number |
| user_metadata | JSONB | { name, role, community_id, company_id } |

**profiles table**:
| Column | Type | Description |
|--------|------|-------------|
| id | UUID | References auth.users (primary key) |
| name | string | User's display name |
| community_id | UUID | References communities.id |
| company_id | string | References companies.id |
| role | string | 'super_admin', 'property_admin', 'resident' |
| created_at | timestamp | Creation timestamp |
| updated_at | timestamp | Last update timestamp |

**resident_details table**:
| Column | Type | Description |
|--------|------|-------------|
| profile_id | UUID | References profiles.id (primary key) |
| building | string | Building name/number |
| floor | string | Floor number |
| unit_number | string | Unit/apartment number |
| parking_space | string | Parking space identifier |
| updated_at | timestamp | Last update timestamp |

**companies table**:
| Column | Type | Description |
|--------|------|-------------|
| id | string | Company unique identifier |
| name | string | Company display name |
| owner_name | string | Owner contact name |
| contact_phone | string | Contact phone number |
| contact_email | string | Contact email address |
| created_at | timestamp | Creation timestamp |
| updated_at | timestamp | Last update timestamp |

**communities table**:
| Column | Type | Description |
|--------|------|-------------|
| id | UUID | Primary key, auto-generated |
| name | string | Community name |
| facilities | JSONB | Array of facility names |
| invite_code | string | Unique 8-char registration code |
| company_id | string | References companies.id |
| created_at | timestamp | Creation timestamp |
| updated_at | timestamp | Last update timestamp |

